# ⚠️ LOCAL ONLY — DO NOT COMMIT OR PUSH

This file marks the project root for private local files.

The following must **never** be pushed to GitHub:

- `.env.local` — Supabase keys and passwords
- `README.md` — private setup & login guide for the family

They are listed in `.gitignore`. If you ever accidentally stage them, run:

```bash
git rm --cached .env.local README.md
```

Only `.env.local.example` (no real secrets) is safe to commit.
